				h2.product__title.js-clean Limited edition
				.product__item.js-clean
					img.product__img.product__img--07(src='./images/products/prod_blue.png')
					.product__descr
						p MONT BLANC
						p vodka VOYAGE 0.7l
						span Limited edition dedicated to the 250th anniversary of the first circumnavigation of the world under the French flag.
				.product__item.js-clean
					img.product__img.product__img--07(src='./images/products/prod_plat.png')
					.product__descr
						p MONT BLANC
						p vodka Pure Diamond 0.7l
						span A limited series dedicated to the first human ascent of Mont Blanc and the first discoveries of valuable crystals and minerals hidden in the glaciers of the Mont Blanc mountain range.

